title: #229 - Someone On The Crew Is A Psychopath & Papa John Calls In
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast we are joined once again by Dr. Drew and Dr. Mark Young to analyze the results of the crew's personality tests. There are some big surprises... including one of us that literally set a record on the test. After that we can a drop in call from the big papa himself- Papa John, to update us on his ongoing battle to bring about the day of reckoning!
